data.description: Inviting 3-Bedroom Home: Modern Updates, Spacious Yard    Discover this charming 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home, nestled in Fair Oaks in Smyrna,  minutes away from The Battery & Truist Park. With hardwood floors throughout the main living areas, the home exudes warmth and charm.  The updated kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and stylish cabinetry, while the adjacent dining area offers a sunny space with plenty of natural light. The expansive fenced backyard, perfect for outdoor entertaining or relaxation.  Three comfortable bedrooms and an updated bathroom with modern fixtures and finishes.   A full refreshed basement offers additional storage space (so much space) and potential for customization, washer and dryer will stay with property.  Enjoy easy access to shopping, dining, and recreational activities nearby, as well as the tranquility of nearby parks and green spaces. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours – schedule a showing today!
